2007-05-08	Anthony Kozar	<anthonykozar@sbcglobal.net>

	* source/BP2/-BP2.h:
	* source/BP2/-BP2decl.h:
	* source/BP2/-BP2main.h:
	* resources/plst-resource.plc:
	* source/BP2/SaveLoads3.c:
		Added a new file type for Midi driver settings (-md, .bpmd, 'BP16').

	* resources/CoreMIDISettings.rsrc:  Load, Save, and Save Startup buttons.
	
	* source/BP2/-BP2.proto.h:
	* source/BP2/CoreMIDIdriver.c:
	* source/BP2/Dialogs.c (DoDialog):
	* source/BP2/Interface1.c (TellOthersMyName):
	* source/BP2/SaveLoads1.c:
		New functions for loading and saving the Midi driver settings.
		Work is divided between SaveLoads1.c which handles the "BP2 side" of
			displaying Open/Save dialogs, opening files, reading and writing
			headers, etc.  The "driver side" code (CoreMIDIdriver.c only
			for now) handles reading and writing only the informations specific
			to that driver's configuration.
		Functions for loading/saving a default "-md.startup" file.

